quran[7{c,v,t}:
2,170,un se jab kaha jata hai ke Allah ne jo ehkaam nazil kiye hain unn ki pairwi karo to jawab dete hain ke hum to isi tareeqay ki pairwi karen ge jis par hum ne apne baap dada ko paaya hai acha agar un ke baap dada ne aqal se kuch bhi kaam nah liya ho aur raah raast nah payi ho to kya phir bhi yeh inhen ki pairwi kiye chalay jayen ge ?
2,171,"yeh log jinhon ne khuda ke betaye hue tareeqay par chalne se inkaar kar diya hai inn ki haalat bilkul aisi hai jaisay charwaha janwaron ko pukaarta hai aur woh haank pukaar ki sada ke siwa kuch nahi suntay yeh behray hain, gungay hain, andhay hain, is liye koi baat un ki samajh mein nahi aati"
2,172,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, agar tum haqeeqat mein Allah ki bandagi karne walay ho to jo pak cheeze hum ne tumhe bakhsh hain unhen be takalouf khao aur Allah ka shukar ada karo"
2,173,"Allah ki taraf se agar koi pabandi tum par hai to woh yeh hai ke Murdaar nah khao, khoon se aur soor ke gosht se parhaiz karo aur koi cheez nah khao jis par Allah ke siwa kisi aur ka naam liya gaya ho haan jo shakhs majaboori ki haalat mein ho aur woh un mein se koi cheez kha le baghair is ke ke woh qanoon shikni ka iradah rakhta ho ya zaroorat ki hadd se tajawaz kar y, to is par kuch gunah nahi, Allah bakhsnay wala aur reham karne wala hai"
2,174,"haq yeh hai ke jo log unn ehkaam ko chupatay hain jo Allah ne apni kitaab mein naz l- kiye hain aur thoray se dunewi faido para nahi bhaint charhatay hain, woh darasal apne pait aag se bhar rahay hain qayamat ke roz Allah hargiz un se baat nah kere ga, nah unhen pakeeza tehra-ay ga, aur unn ke liye dard naak saza hai"
2,175,yeh woh log hain jinhon ne hadaayat ke badlay zala-lat khareedi aur mughfirat ke badlay azaab mol le liya kaisa ajeeb hai un ka hosla ke jahannum ka azaab bardasht karne ke liye tayyar hain
2,176,yeh sab kuch is wajah se howa ke Allah ne to theek theek haq ke mutabiq kitaab nazil ki thi magar jin logon ne kitaab mein ikhtilaaf nikalay woh apne jhagron mein haq se bohat daur nikal gay
